# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# NOTE on keystore policy:
#   The committed keystore at app/mytube.keystore is INTENTIONALLY tracked
#   because this is a private repo for an offline app. If you ever fork this
#   into a public repo, generate a NEW keystore locally, replace the file,
#   update the credentials in app/build.gradle, and never push the old one.
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
